    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://openrouter.ai/api/v1/chat/completions",
        "authentication": "predefinedCredentialType",
        "nodeCredentialType": "openRouterApi",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"model\": \"openai/gpt-5.4\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"system\",\n      \"content\": \"You generate image prompts for a sleep YouTube channel. Each prompt describes a unique dark oil painting scene related to the given topic.\\n\\nSTYLE (apply to every prompt):\\n- Dark oil painting style, old masters aesthetic (Rembrandt, Caravaggio)\\n- Thick visible brushstrokes, impasto texture\\n- Dramatic chiaroscuro lighting, deep blacks with a single soft warm light source\\n- Color palette: deep blacks, deep navy, dark teal, deep ocean blues and greens, hints of dark purple\\n- Calm, still, peaceful compositions only\\n- Always end every prompt with: dark oil painting, old masters aesthetic, no text\\n\\nCOMPOSITION VARIETY - distribute evenly across all 30 prompts:\\n- Wide establishing shots\\n- Close-up portraits of face or single feature\\n- Overhead top-down views\\n- Side profile compositions\\n- Silhouette with faint backlight\\n- Subject small within large dark habitat\\n- Macro detail shots of texture, eye, or skin\\n\\nRESTRICTIONS:\\n- NO violence, predation, or scary elements\\n- NO bright or saturated colors\\n- NO readable text in images\\n\\nOUTPUT FORMAT:\\nGenerate EXACTLY {{ $json.image_count }} prompts.\\nOutput ONLY a valid JSON array, no markdown, no explanation:\\n[{\\\"prompt\\\": \\\"A dark oil painting of...\\\"}, {\\\"prompt\\\": \\\"A dark oil painting of...\\\"}]\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": {{ JSON.stringify($json.topic) }}\n    }\n  ],\n  \"temperature\": 1,\n  \"max_tokens\": 280000\n}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "586bc98e-fa75-46d1-8b4f-4108649cd063",
      "name": "Generate Prompts via OpenAI",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        208,
        160
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "openRouterApi": {
          "id": "VNgbdBR86ZkDETr5",
          "name": "OpenRouter account"
        }
      },
      "notes": "Creates all image prompts for this chapter"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const openaiResponse = $input.item.json.choices[0].message.content;\nlet prompts;\n\ntry {\n  prompts = JSON.parse(openaiResponse);\n} catch (e) {\n  const jsonMatch = openaiResponse.match(/```json\\s*([\\s\\S]*?)\\s*```/);\n  if (jsonMatch) {\n    prompts = JSON.parse(jsonMatch[1]);\n  } else {\n    throw new Error(\"Could not parse OpenAI response as JSON\");\n  }\n}\n\nconst videoName = $('Loop Over Topics').item.json.video_name;\nconst rowNumber = $('Loop Over Topics').item.json.row_number;\n\nreturn prompts.map((p, index) => ({\n  json: {\n    video_name: videoName,\n    image_number: String(index + 1).padStart(2, '0'),\n    filename: `${videoName}-${String(index + 1).padStart(2, '0')}.png`,\n    prompt: p.prompt,\n    status: 'pending',\n    topic_row_number: rowNumber\n  }\n}));"
      },
